  "title": "Hair Salon Manager",
  "description": "<p>• Provides services to clients such as cutting, wash & blow, coloring/highlight, hair and scalp treatment</p><p>• Conducting professional hair and scalp analysis, demonstrate features and benefits of products.</p><p>• Explaining of company’s products, treatments processes</p><p>• Emphasizes product benefits and assist clients in the selection of retail products or services for their hair/ scalp care needs</p><p>• Attending clients with professionalism & care, while maintaining good relationship with clients</p><p>• Carry out ad-hoc duties and managerial duties <br /><br />• Oversee staff duties and resolve accordingly<br /><br />• Report sales data and conduct analysis for better sales strategy.<br /><br />• Conduct training for new staff. </p><p><br /></p><p>At least 1-2 years of Hair & Scalp Styling/therapist experience</p><p></p><p><u><strong></strong></u></p>",
